flowchart TD
    A[User Opens Task] --> B[View Subtasks]
    B --> C{User Type?}
    
    C -->|Parent| P1[Add Subtasks]
    P1 --> P2[Edit Subtasks]
    P2 --> P3[Delete Subtasks]
    P3 --> P4[Monitor Progress]
    
    C -->|Child| C1[View Assigned Subtasks]
    C1 --> C2[Complete Subtask]
    C2 --> C3[Update Progress]
    C3 --> C4[See Completion %]
    
    C -->|Individual| I1[Manage Own Subtasks]
    I1 --> I2[Add Subtask]
    I2 --> I3[Complete Subtask]
    I3 --> I4[Track Progress]
    
    P4 --> P1
    C4 --> C1
    I4 --> I1
